Job Details
It sales executive wanted for an it solutions company in sharjah. We are looking for high experienced sales executive who has good knkwledge of IT solutions. You must have three years of experience out of which two years must be in sales. Your job includes product presentation, sales and client account management. Please note this job is not for freshers.
Requirements
3 years minimum experience 2 years atleast in IT sales IT product knowledge Driving license
